---
import ResendCube from './ResendCube.astro';
---

<section class="section about" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-title">
  <div class="site-container about-header" data-motion="row">
    <p class="section-label">02 / Вместе к результату</p>
    <span>Ваша идея остаётся в центре</span>
  </div>

  <div class="site-container about-layout">
    <h2 id="about-title" data-motion="clip">
      <span>Вы приносите мечту.</span>
      <span>Я превращаю её в систему.</span>
      <span>От первого смысла</span>
      <span>до уверенного запуска.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="about-object" data-sequence aria-hidden="true">
      <ResendCube />
    </div>

    <div class="about-copy" data-motion="text">
      <p>Вы рассказываете, куда хотите прийти. Я помогаю увидеть сильную суть идеи и собираю всё необходимое — от структуры и визуального языка до разработки и запуска.</p>
      <p>Мы работаем напрямую, поэтому замысел не теряется между людьми, а каждый шаг ведёт к продукту, которым хочется гордиться.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="site-container about-principles" data-sequence>
    <article data-motion="row"><span>01</span><strong>Слышу вашу цель</strong><i aria-hidden="true"></i></article>
    <article data-motion="row" data-motion-delay="70"><span>02</span><strong>Усиливаю идею</strong><i aria-hidden="true"></i></article>
    <article data-motion="row" data-motion-delay="140"><span>03</span><strong>Показываю движение</strong><i aria-hidden="true"></i></article>
    <article data-motion="row" data-motion-delay="210"><span>04</span><strong>Довожу до запуска</strong><i aria-hidden="true"></i></article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: -1px;
    padding: clamp(7rem, 9vw, 9.5rem) 0 clamp(5.5rem, 7vw, 7.5rem);
    background: transparent;
  }

  .about-header {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-header .section-label { margin: 0; }
  .about-header > span { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.62rem; }
  .about-layout { position: relative; display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.45fr) minmax(18rem, 0.55fr); align-items: center; gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 7rem); margin-top: clamp(2.5rem, 4.5vw, 4.5rem); }
  .about-layout::after { position: absolute; z-index: -1; top: 3%; right: -8%; width: clamp(22rem, 42vw, 42rem); aspect-ratio: 1; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(243, 240, 232, 0.17), rgba(228, 185, 31, 0.08) 34%, transparent 69%); content: ''; filter: blur(1.5rem); animation: about-halo 7s ease-in-out infinite alternate; }

  .about h2 {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    display: grid;
    min-width: 0;
    grid-column: auto;
    max-width: 62rem;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5.55vw, 5.95rem);
    font-weight: 485;
    line-height: 0.93;
    letter-spacing: -0.058em;
  }

  .about h2 span:nth-child(2) { padding-left: 3vw; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .about h2 span:nth-child(3),
  .about h2 span:nth-child(4) { padding-left: 0.75vw; }
  .about-copy { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 52rem; grid-column: 1; padding: 0 0 0.4rem clamp(0rem, 5vw, 5rem); }
  .about-copy p { margin: 0; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: clamp(0.86rem, 1.05vw, 0.98rem); line-height: 1.65; }
  .about-copy p + p { margin-top: 0.9rem; }

  .about-object {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: grid;
    width: min(100%, 31rem);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    grid-column: 2;
    grid-row: 1 / span 2;
    place-items: center;
  }

  @keyframes about-halo { to { translate: -4% 5%; scale: 1.08; opacity: 0.72; } }

  .about-principles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    margin-top: clamp(3.5rem, 5.5vw, 5.5rem);
  }

  .about-principles article {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    min-height: 7rem;
    align-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem 1.25rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    transition: color 500ms var(--ease-out), transform 600ms var(--ease-out), box-shadow 600ms var(--ease-out);
  }

  .about-principles article::before { position: absolute; inset: 0; border-radius: inherit; background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 120%, rgba(181, 31, 43, 0.34), transparent 45%), radial-gradient(circle at 86% -20%, rgba(228, 185, 31, 0.24), transparent 42%), var(--dark); content: ''; opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.94) translateY(0.5rem); transition: opacity 500ms ease, transform 620ms var(--ease-out); }
  .about-principles article > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .about-principles article > span { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.52rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; }
  .about-principles strong { max-width: 12rem; font-size: clamp(0.82rem, 1.1vw, 1rem); font-weight: 620; line-height: 1.25; }
  .about-principles i { width: 2.75rem; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red), #d9d6ce, var(--yellow)); transition: width 600ms var(--ease-out); }
  .about-principles article:hover { color: var(--white); box-shadow: 0 1.4rem 3rem rgba(17, 19, 23, 0.12); transform: translateY(-0.3rem); }
  .about-principles article:hover::before { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  .about-principles article:hover i { width: 100%; }

  @media (max-width: 63.99rem) {
    .about-layout { grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.25fr) minmax(15rem, 0.75fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .about-copy { margin-top: 1.5rem; padding-left: 0; }
    .about-object { width: min(100%, 24rem); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 47.99rem) {
    .about { padding: 7.5rem 0 8.5rem; }
    .about-header > span { display: none; }
    .about h2 { font-size: clamp(2.85rem, 13.5vw, 4.5rem); }
    .about h2 span:nth-child(2),
    .about h2 span:nth-child(3),
    .about h2 span:nth-child(4) { padding-left: 0; }
    .about-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-object { grid-column: 1; grid-row: auto; width: min(21rem, 88vw); margin: 0 auto; }
    .about-copy { grid-column: 1; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
    .about-principles { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); margin-top: 3rem; }
    .about-principles article { min-height: 6.5rem; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .about-principles article { transition: none; }
    .about-layout::after { animation: none; }
  }
</style>
